data.description: Welcome home! 2280 Josephine Road is the perfect definition of peaceful living! This beautiful property located in Scott County includes a 2020 manufactured home (on permanent foundation) with three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, eat-in kitchen, spacious closets, and utility room. This move-in ready home sits on 6.3 acres and includes a chicken coop! All appliances will remain. Property is less than 30 minutes from Georgetown, less than 45 minutes from Lexington and Frankfort. If you’re looking for relaxation, privacy, and space, this one is for you!
